---
title: Linked List  |  Access O(n) · Prepend O(1) · Traverse O(n)
---
graph LR
    classDef headTail fill:#22c55e,stroke:#15803d,color:#fff
    classDef node fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff
    classDef nullNode fill:#ef4444,stroke:#b91c1c,color:#fff

    head(["head"]):::headTail --> N1["Node · value=1"]:::node
    N1 -->|next| N2["Node · value=2"]:::node
    N2 -->|next| N3["Node · value=3"]:::node
    N3 -->|next| NULL(["null"]):::nullNode
